Available commands

c1  Command 1 a file.
    
    c1 <filename> [options]
    
    Parameters:
    
    filename  The name of the file.
    
    Options:
    
    /delete   Delete the file after processing.
    /archive  Archive after processing

c2  Command 2 an archive
    
    c2 <name> <keep> [options]
    
    Parameters:
    
    name  The name of the archive.
    keep  The number of days to keep the archive
    
    Options:
    
    /maxSize  The maximum size of the archive.

c3  Generate loads of spam
    
    c3 <iterations> <Message> <OverrunLength>
    
    Parameters:
    
    iterations     Number of times to repeat
    Message        The message to spam.
    OverrunLength  Amount packet should be longer
                   than it claims

